# Proptest Regression Seeds
#
# This directory contains regression seeds discovered by proptest fuzzing.
# These files are INTENTIONALLY COMMITTED to the repository.
#
# Each .txt file represents a counterexample that caused a test failure.
# By committing these, we ensure:
# 1. The same edge case is tested deterministically in every CI run
# 2. The "immunity" is shared across all contributors
# 3. We can track when a regression was introduced/fixed
#
# Do NOT add this directory to .gitignore.
